  m_text: "\n\n\n\nIf anyone reads this\nIm all alone now.\nThere is something out
    there.\nI heard it again tonight. Not pipes. Not wind.\LScratching. Moving. Hunting.\nThe
    storm stills and the radio cuts off.\nCant call for help.\nCant run."
